```

You must understand:

ğŸ‘‰ If destination is NOT in my local network
ğŸ‘‰ Send packet to 172.27.96.1
ğŸ‘‰ Through eth0

172.27.96.1 = Gateway

ğŸ”¥ Very important concept.

---

# âœ… 4ï¸âƒ£ What is Local Route?

From your output:

```bash
